cs|1|at|The convention we are about to present was developed by ^*BBridge Base Inc.^*N President, ^*BFred Gitelman^*N and his regular partner ^*BBrad Moss^*N. It is entirely possible (if not likely) that somebody else has independently come up with this idea before, but to the best of our knowledge what you are about to read is an original idea.

{ ^*BWarning!!!^*N } @2We think this is a great idea, but we do not recommend adopting this convention in a casual partnership or if you are an inexperienced player. If you decide that you want to try out this convention make sure you discuss the followup auctions thoroughly with your regular partner. The same general advice should apply to ^*Iany^*N new convention that you want to adopt.

@0
